description.narrative:
1. Encourage economic development of SMEs all of which will be located in IDA countries by investing in 50 high-growth companies which is expected to lead to above average rates of job creation, capacity development and higher tax revenue;
2. Improve companies sustainable development by helping implement best practice corporate governance and environmental and social standards;
3. Provide much needed business services support funding to help companies become stronger, and
4. Provide support to a new fund manager that is launching a private equity fund.
